---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Journal
description: Notes on slow living from Maya Renn — rituals, recipes, and soft interiors.
permalink: /blog/
---
<div class="wrap">
  <header class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Journal</p>
    <h1>Notes on living slowly</h1>
    <p class="lede">Small essays on rituals, simple food, and rooms that breathe. New entries most Sundays.</p>
  </header>

  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li>
      <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
      <div>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
